snippet: Four dancers celebrate Swedish culture with offerings of elegance, strength and tenacity.
abstract: Gia Kourlas reviews dance program The Nordic Body: Choreographers From the Land of the Midnight Sun, featuring performances by Helena Franzen, Irene Hultman, My Lindblad and SU-EN Butoh Company, at 92nd Street Y as part of its Dig Dance series.
lead_paragraph: Four dancers celebrate Swedish culture with offerings of elegance, strength and tenacity.

headline.main: Review: ‘The Nordic Body’ Moves at 92nd Street Y
headline.print_headline: A Sweeping Tour of Sweden Onstage
